structure.unit: FEES AND COMPENSATION OF PUBLIC OFFICERS AND EMPLOYEES

law.history: Repealed 1950 Ky. Acts ch. 123, sec. 29. -- Created 1946 Ky. Acts ch. 92, sec. 1.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Sheriffs in certain counties containing second-class city, population between 70,000 and 75,000, and valuation less than $100,000,000.
